				\usepackage{amsmath}
				\usepackage{wasysym}
				\usepackage{amsfonts}
				\usepackage{amssymb}
				\usepackage{amsbsy}
				\usepackage{mathrsfs}
				\usepackage{upgreek}
				\setlength{\oddsidemargin}{-69pt}
				\begin{document}$$1840\,^\circ \text {C}$$\end{document}29,42 and the absorption band in the UV region, TiO2\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
				\usepackage{amsmath}
